/-! ### Relationship with entropy via covers -/

variable [UniformSpace X] (T : X ‚Üí X) (F : Set X)

/-- Bowen-Dinaburg's definition of topological entropy using packings is
  `‚®Ü U ‚àà ùì§ X, packingEntropyEntourage T F U`. This quantity is the same as the topological entropy
